Package: cogserver
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libatomspace (>= 5.0.5),
         libatomspace-storage (>= 5.0.5),
         libcogutil (>= 1.0.0),
         libzmq3
Description: OpenCog CogServer networking and server (executable)
 CogServer provides the networking and server infrastructure for the
 OpenCog cognitive architecture, enabling distributed reasoning and
 remote access to AtomSpace.
 .
 This package contains the CogServer executable and utilities.

